## What's Changed
* feat: Add --no-spawn-shell flag to disable shell access by @ShivamB25 in https://github.com/dundee/gdu/pull/440
* feat: Add --reverse-sort flag for non-interactive mode by @ShivamB25 in https://github.com/dundee/gdu/pull/436
* feat: switch mouse flag name, mimic default ncdu behavior by @shantanugadgil in https://github.com/dundee/gdu/pull/420
* feat: bump version of tcell, drop support for Golang 1.22 by @dundee in https://github.com/dundee/gdu/pull/432
* fix: make 'no' the default button in delete/empty confirmation dialogs by @ShivamB25 in https://github.com/dundee/gdu/pull/437
* fix: reorder `--mouse` option by @shantanugadgil in https://github.com/dundee/gdu/pull/433
* fix: ulikunitz/xz package update to fix vulnerability by @jullianow in https://github.com/dundee/gdu/pull/446
* ci: use Golang 1.24.4 by @shantanugadgil in https://github.com/dundee/gdu/pull/421
* refactor: struct align by @dundee in https://github.com/dundee/gdu/pull/442
* docs: fix link to configuration.md by @joliss in https://github.com/dundee/gdu/pull/392

## New Contributors
* @shantanugadgil made their first contribution in https://github.com/dundee/gdu/pull/420
* @jullianow made their first contribution in https://github.com/dundee/gdu/pull/446
* @joliss made their first contribution in https://github.com/dundee/gdu/pull/392

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/dundee/gdu/compare/v5.31.0...v5.32.0
